flowchart TD
    A[User Strategic Prompt] --> B[main.py: Load Config + CostGuard]
    B --> C[Initialize GeminiClient with cache + guard]
    C --> C1["Enable prompt logging → outputs/prompt_log_{ts}.jsonl"]
    C1 --> C2["Enable file logging → outputs/execution_log_{ts}.txt"]
    C2 --> D[Seed GraphMemory with known edges]

    D --> E[Construct Agent Team]
    E --> F["AnalystAgent.run(prompt)"]

    %% ── Planning ──
    F --> G["Step 1: build_plan() — LLM decomposes prompt"]
    G --> H["Step 2: NewsAndDataAgent.fetch_and_index()"]

    %% ── Real data fetching ──
    H --> H1["Gemini Google-Search Grounding — 6 queries (in-memory)"]
    H --> H2["SEC EDGAR XBRL — GOOGL, MSFT, AMZN (in-memory, not persisted)"]
    H --> H3[SEC EDGAR Full-Text Search]
    H --> H4[Google News RSS — 4 queries]

    H1 --> I[Raw Documents — in-memory]
    H2 --> I
    H3 --> I
    H4 --> I

    %% ── Retrieval pipeline ──
    I --> J[Chunker: sentence-aware, overlap]
    J --> K[Metadata Enricher: company, topic, date]
    K --> L1["BM25 Sparse Index (in-memory)"]
    K --> L2["Gemini Embedding Dense Index (in-memory, API responses cached in .cache/gemini/)"]
    L1 --> M[Hybrid Index: RRF Fusion]
    L2 --> M

    %% ── Query phase ──
    M --> N["Step 3: Retrieve financial context"]
    N --> O[LLM Reranker: score 0-1, drop < 0.35]
    O --> P[Context Fuser: de-dup + token budget]

    %% ── Analysis ──
    P --> Q["Step 4: LLM extracts structured financials"]
    Q --> R["Step 5: Dynamic tool — market share delta"]
    R --> S["Step 6: Retrieve qualitative signals"]
    S --> T["Step 7: Read GraphMemory context"]
    T --> U["Step 8: LLM threat analysis"]

    %% ── Critique loop ──
    U --> V["Step 9: CritiqueModule — rubric scoring"]
    V --> W{Verdict?}
    W -->|PASS| X["Step 11: LLM generate 3 strategies"]
    W -->|NEEDS_REFINEMENT| Y["Step 10: LLM refinement queries"]
    Y --> Z[Re-retrieve + re-analyse]
    Z --> V

    %% ── Synthesis ──
    X --> AA["Step 12: LLM extracts memory edges"]
    AA --> BB["Step 13: LLM executive summary"]
    BB --> CC[main.py: render_report]
    CC --> DD["Write outputs/strategic_report.md"]
    CC --> EE["Write outputs/raw_result.json"]
    DD --> FF[Print Cost Summary]
    EE --> FF

    %% ── Logging: every LLM call logs to prompt_log JSONL ──
    G -.->|"log prompt #1"| C1
    H1 -.->|"log prompts #2-7"| C1
    O -.->|"log prompts #8-9, #11-12"| C1
    Q -.->|"log prompt #10"| C1
    U -.->|"log prompt #13"| C1
    V -.->|"log prompt #14"| C1
    X -.->|"log prompt #15"| C1
    AA -.->|"log prompt #16"| C1
    BB -.->|"log prompt #17"| C1

    %% ── Styles ──
    style C fill:#2d6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style FF fill:#d62,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style C1 fill:#36c,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style C2 fill:#36c,stroke:#333,color:#fff
